posts.content:
Hello Mike,

Thank you for reaching out to Hallmark Consumer Care.

We completely understand your reasons for contacting us today and are sorry for the inconvenience this may cause. We appreciate the opportunity to clarify any price adjustments for you.

Hallmark's dedication to helping our consumers celebrate life's meaningful moments remains our focus. We are committed to maintaining fair pricing across our portfolio and are fortunate to manufacture a large percentage of our products in Kansas-based manufacturing facilities. As we look toward the important holiday season, we've made the necessary decision to adjust pricing on select products from our gift and ornaments collections that are impacted by the current economic climate.

We would also like to share that we have seen an expression of interest in layaway this year. We encourage you to ask about these options at your next visit to a participating Gold Crown store. It is a great way to still earn bonus points as well as additional time to complete the transaction for your wish list items.

We're here to help, and we appreciate your loyalty to Hallmark.

Best,

Hallmark Care 1-800-HALLMARK (1-800-425-5627) care.hallmark.com
